This paper deals with propositional solvers and problem solving, which are typically associated with artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic (cs.LO). The use of unit propagation is a technique commonly used in constraint satisfaction problems, which falls under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). The paper also discusses implementation and experimental study, which are associated with programming languages (cs.PL) and data mining (cs.DM).
